      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver for anyone looking for functional transportation. While the engine and transmission are in good working order, the car does show its age with some noticeable cosmetic wear on the interior upholstery and a few minor exterior scuffs. It has been regularly maintained, though a few non-essential features may require attention soon. It\u2019s a solid, honest car for someone who prioritizes reliability over a perfect appearance.",
